timers.name: sh: ps -AF | grep ${{RUNTIME.targetJar}} | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}'
Sh-invoke:ps -AF | grep quarkus-io-thread-runner.jar | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}'
Sh-await-callback:ps -AF | grep quarkus-io-thread-runner.jar | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}'
sh: ps -AF | grep quarkus-io-thread-runner.jar | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}'
Sh-invoke:ps -AF | grep quarkus-worker-pool-runner.jar | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}'
Sh-await-callback:ps -AF | grep quarkus-worker-pool-runner.jar | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}'

sh: for i in  $(seq 1 ${{TEST_ITERATIONS}}); do eval node scripts/timing/time.js ${{RUNTIME.name}}/target/${{RUNTIME.targetJar}} >> ${{SERVER_FILE_PATH}}/output/${{RUNTIME.name}}.timeFirstRequest.out; done

Sh-invoke:for i in  $(seq 1 5); do eval node scripts/timing/time.js quarkus-io-thread/target/quarkus-io-thread-runner.jar >> /tmp/quarkus-test/server/output/quarkus-io-thread.timeFirstRequest.out; done

Sh-await-callback:for i in  $(seq 1 5); do eval node scripts/timing/time.js quarkus-io-thread/target/quarkus-io-thread-runner.jar >> /tmp/quarkus-test/server/output/quarkus-io-thread.timeFirstRequest.out; done
sh: for i in  $(seq 1 5); do eval node scripts/timing/time.js quarkus-io-thread/target/quarkus-io-thread-runner.jar >> /tmp/quarkus-test/server/output/quarkus-io-thread.timeFirstRequest.out; done

Sh-invoke:for i in  $(seq 1 5); do eval node scripts/timing/time.js quarkus-worker-pool/target/quarkus-worker-pool-runner.jar >> /tmp/quarkus-test/server/output/quarkus-worker-pool.timeFirstRequest.out; done

Sh-await-callback:for i in  $(seq 1 5); do eval node scripts/timing/time.js quarkus-worker-pool/target/quarkus-worker-pool-runner.jar >> /tmp/quarkus-test/server/output/quarkus-worker-pool.timeFirstRequest.out; done
